parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the footwell control module can cause various electrical systems to malfunction, including turn signals, brake lights, windows, and dashboard functions, which can lead to safety hazards and accidents.
symptoms: Unknown warning lights illuminated
turn signal became inoperable
windows failed to roll up or down
message to "Take Vehicle to BMW Dealer Immediately" displayed
footwell control module failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delayed availability of parts for the recall repair can leave vehicles vulnerable to electrical system failures, which can cause safety hazards and accidents.
symptoms: No symptoms reported
but delayed recall repair can lead to potential electrical system failures.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Pump Relay Circuit Board Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump relay circuit board can cause the vehicle to stall and die on the road, which can lead to safety hazards and accidents.
symptoms: Vehicle intermittently stalls and dies on the road
no warning lights or codes stored in the computer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine operational failure can cause the vehicle to stall and lose power, which can lead to safety hazards and accidents.
symptoms: Engine malfunction indicator lamp comes on
vehicle stalls and stops in traffic
reduced or complete loss of power
requires powering off for 5-15 minutes to restart.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cup holder electrical short can cause an electrical component to fail, which can lead to safety hazards and accidents.
symptoms: Cup holder leaks and shorts out an electrical component that controls the gear shift knob.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The speedometer inaccuracy can cause drivers to misjudge their speed, which can lead to safety hazards and accidents.
symptoms: Speedometer indicates a speed that is 8% over actual.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The window malfunction can cause inconvenience and potentially lead to safety hazards if the window becomes stuck in a position that obstructs the driver's view.
symptoms: Window stopped working
one-touch feature stopped working
faint clicking sound heard from the driver's door/footwell area.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger seat occupancy sensor can cause the passenger airbag to malfunction, leading to potential injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates on the instrument panel
the passenger airbag does not deploy
the seat belt light comes on
a message appears indicating the passenger seat airbag will not deploy
the airbag warning light turns on and off periodically.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden failure of the engine freeze plug can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to potential accidents or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls while driving
often without warning
and may be accompanied by a sudden loss of power or unusual noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Water Ingress and Electrical System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water ingress into the vehicle can cause electrical system failures, leading to loss of critical safety features, such as all-wheel drive, and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: Water accumulation in the trunk or rear seat area
often accompanied by electrical system malfunctions
such as faulty computer systems or warning lights.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Gear Shifter Failure due to Liquid Ingress
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Liquid ingress into the gear shifter can cause it to malfunction, leading to difficulties shifting gears, and potentially causing accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The gear shifter becomes stuck or difficult to operate
often accompanied by unusual noises or warning lights.
